<Defs>

  <ThingDef ParentName="AnimalThingBase">
    <defName>FEB_Gutterhog</defName>
    <label>gutterhog</label>
    <description>Gutterhogs were originally bred for minefield cleanup and searching for unexploded ordinance. While most have since gone feral, they still retain a powerful urge to dig up metal objects. For this reason they gravitate towards ruins and are popular pets among scavengers.</description>
